description: Miklós Felvidéki is a Fumetto award winner Hungarian illustrator and comic book artist who also works in animation. His work appeared in several Hungarian and Eastern European comic book anthologies and stand alone publications. He also worked on Josh Tierney's collaborative web comic series Spera.
name: Miklós Felvidéki

deck: Benicio Del Toro will play the Collector in Thor: The Dark World and Guardians of the Galaxy.
description:
His full name is Benicio Monserrate Rafael del Toro Sánchez.

He played "Jackie Boy" the 2005 film Sin City and the Collector in Thor: The Dark World and Guardians of the Galaxy.
name: Benicio Del Toro

description:
Djimon Hounsou is a Beninese actor and former fashion model who has been nominated for two Academy Awards for his performances in In America and Blood Diamond.

In terms of comic book roles, he is known for voicing Black Panther in the BET animated series, and for playing Korath the Pursuer in Guardians of the Galaxy.
name: Djimon Hounsou

description: A Scottish actress best known for playing Amy Pond in Doctor Who and Nebula in Guardians of the Galaxy.
